{
  "text": "NDT80 system was carried out as described [CITATION_1] . In brief, sporulation was induced as described. At 6 h postinduction, β-estradiol was added to 2 μM to induce expression of NDT80. Ime2-as1 was inhibited by adding Bn-PP1 (a generous gift from Kevin Shokat, University of California, San Francisco, CA) to 10 μm. Plasmids used in this study are listed in Table 2 .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "206826751"
